<Link id="l00787" /><CodeLine lineNumber="787"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00788" /><CodeLine lineNumber="788"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// MO&#95;PAGE - A symbol operand with this flag represents the pc-relative</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00789" /><CodeLine lineNumber="789"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// offset of the 4K page containing the symbol.  This is used with the</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00790" /><CodeLine lineNumber="790"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// ADRP instruction.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00791" /><CodeLine lineNumber="791" lineLink="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/aarch64ii/#ae22a65863fdb02ce99abf9ee08bcbb71a7f04634c15a04a59d5f234002e613b5b"><Highlight kind="normal">  <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/aarch64ii/#ae22a65863fdb02ce99abf9ee08bcbb71a7f04634c15a04a59d5f234002e613b5b">MO&#95;PAGE</a> = 1,</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00792" /><CodeLine lineNumber="792"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00793" /><CodeLine lineNumber="793"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// MO&#95;PAGEOFF - A symbol operand with this flag represents the offset of</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00794" /><CodeLine lineNumber="794"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// that symbol within a 4K page.  This offset is added to the page address</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00797" /><CodeLine lineNumber="797"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00798" /><CodeLine lineNumber="798"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// MO&#95;G3 - A symbol operand with this flag (granule 3) represents the high</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00813" /><CodeLine lineNumber="813"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00814" /><CodeLine lineNumber="814"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// MO&#95;HI12 - This flag indicates that a symbol operand represents the bits</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00817" /><CodeLine lineNumber="817" lineLink="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/aarch64ii/#ae22a65863fdb02ce99abf9ee08bcbb71abb4faac7fe2138d41464b4e802ec103f"><Highlight kind="normal">  <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/aarch64ii/#ae22a65863fdb02ce99abf9ee08bcbb71abb4faac7fe2138d41464b4e802ec103f">MO&#95;HI12</a> = 7,</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00818" /><CodeLine lineNumber="818"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00819" /><CodeLine lineNumber="819"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// MO&#95;COFFSTUB - On a symbol operand &quot;FOO&quot;, this indicates that the</Highlight></CodeLine>
